    "col_intro_title": "What is this site about",
    "col_intro_text": "In this site, I'm presenting some of my current interests on what to pursue in my life. The motivation is to gain feedback, reach possible collaborators and to fing funding/employment avenus. Also, if you are pursuing some of the things presented here, I could be interested in giving you feedback.\n\nDepending on how they are written, some plans for texts can also act as drafts for the text and can be continuously improved until they can be published as finalized texts. Having the plans/drafts public makes me more motivated to focus on them at that stage, since I know they can be seen and to have some kind of impact already. This increased focus increases the probability that the plans/drafts will become final texts at some points. \n\nMy possible interests are not limited to the ones presented here, but I hope they  can be used to give some kind of impression of me in general and what else I could be interested in. \n\n------\nThe site has been vibecoded with Claude. ",
    "details_title": "Descriptions",
    "details_hint": "Click on a topic in the graph to see details here",
    "vote_title": "Influence my focus",
    "vote_text": "What themes, projects or skills do you think I should pursue? What would be necessary or what would I be good at, for example. \n\nYou can vote here: https://forms.gle/XR1jRv25ng2Ky5SE6\n\nI'll take your opinions into account. Form also has an open field that you can use how you wish. ",
    "funding_title": "Funding/work opportunities",
    "funding_intro": "Currently I'm pursuing these interests on my own time but I'm also looking for work/funding. Feel free to contact me with suggestions regarding work on these intererests or anything else you think I might be interested in. \n\nHere is my current preference order for different funding sources:",
